NAME
    retrorig-setup - a convenient debian package to install all necessary files to
    install retrorig.

SYNOPSIS
    sudo retrorig-setup
    su -c retrorig-setup

DESCRIPTION
    This setup package will install all necessary setup files for users to configure
    and install retrorig itself.

OPTIONS
    TO-DO
    
